<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Kanglung Dine</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/header.css"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/footer.css"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <!-- ===== NAVBAR ===== -->
  <%- include('components/header') %>

  <!-- ===== HERO SECTION ===== -->
  <section class="hero-section">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Discover the Best Eateries in Kanglung</h1>
      <p>Browse, locate, and reserve your favorite spots to eat with ease.</p>
      <form class="search-bar" action="/search" method="GET">
        <input type="text" name="q" placeholder="Search restaurants..." required />
        <button type="submit">Search</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CATEGORIES / FEATURED ===== -->
<section class="categories">
    <h2>Top Categories</h2>
    <div class="category-grid">
      <div class="category-card">
        <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.ujsMXfsctykenHPtlmUYiQHaEK?w=250&h=180&c=7&r=0&o=5&pid=1.7" alt="Cafés" class="category-img" />
        <div>Cafés</div>
      </div>
      <div class="category-card">
        <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.TOIKvxylk601phktsEXgLAHaEU?w=296&h=180&c=7&r=0&o=5&pid=1.7" alt="Restaurants" class="category-img" />
        <div>Restaurants</div>
      </div>
      <div class="category-card">
        <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.lRc4os3fson9Alq66FTZSAHaFc?w=226&h=180&c=7&r=0&o=5&pid=1.7" alt="Fast Food" class="category-img" />
        <div>Bar</div>
      </div>
      <div class="category-card">
        <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.Udnr9WHfF_ZA4w_BYVhLwAHaLG?w=115&h=180&c=7&r=0&o=5&pid=1.7" alt="Bakery" class="category-img" />
        <div>Bakery</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- ===== VISUAL FEST ===== -->
<section class="visual-fest">
    <div class="visual-container">
      <div class="visual-images">
        <img src="/images/home_VF1.jpeg" alt="Bhutanese dumplings">
        <img src="/images/home_VF2.jpeg" alt="Bhutanese Food">
        <img src="/images/home_VF3.jpeg" alt="Bhutanese Food">
        <img src="/images/home_VF4.jpeg" alt="Bhutanese Food">
        <img src="/images/home_VF5.jpeg" alt="Bhutanese Food">
        <img src="/images/home_VF6.jpeg" alt="Bhutanese Food">
        <img src="/images/home_VF7.jpeg" alt="Bhutanese Food">
        <img src="/images/home_VF8.jpeg" alt="Bhutanese Food">
      </div>
      <div class="visual-text">
        <h2>Visual Fest</h2>
        <p><strong>Take a Glimpse of the mouthwatering creations<br> from Kanglung, Trashigang</strong></p>
        <button class="btn-view">View More</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- ===== TESTIMONIALS ===== -->
  <section class="testimonials">
    <h2>TESTIMONIALS & REVIEWS</h2>
    <div class="testimonial-cards">
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <p>A good restaurant is like a vacation; it transports you, and it becomes a lot more than just about the food. All great deeds and all great thoughts</p>
        <h4>Sangay Lhazom</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <p>A good restaurant is like a vacation; it transports you, and it becomes a lot more than just about the food. All great deeds and all great thoughts</p>
        <h4>Sangay Dendup</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <p>A good restaurant is like a vacation; it transports you, and it becomes a lot more than just about the food. All great deeds and all great thoughts</p>
        <h4>Dechen Dorji</h4>
      </div>
    </div>
    <button class="btn-view">View More</button>
  </section>  
  

  <!-- ===== FOOTER ===== -->
  <%- include('components/footer') %>

  <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
